row.InputSentence1: Our parents took us to Paragon Park in 1963.
row.InputSentence2: We took a ferry from Rowes Wharf in Boston.
row.InputSentence3: We rode the carousel, the whip, and the caterpillar.
row.RandomFifthSentenceQuiz1: We have many fond memories of this childhood trip.
